## 4. Audit & Laporan Keuangan (Financial Reports)

**Source file**: [auditData.js](file:///home/user/Documents/Github/frontend-perempuanaman/data/auditData.js) — 7 reports with PDFs

**Frontend pages**: `/kerja-kami/audit`, `/kerja-kami/audit/[slug]` (uses `FlipbookViewer`)

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/audit` | 🔓 | List all audit documents |
| GET | `/api/audit/:slug` | 🔓 | Single audit document |
| POST | `/api/audit` | 🔒 | Create (with PDF upload) |
| PUT | `/api/audit/:id` | 🔒 | Update |
| DELETE | `/api/audit/:id` | 🔒 | Delete |

**Data shape**:
