## 5. Wilayah Organisasi (Regional Map & Statistics)

**Source file**: [wilayahData.js](file:///home/user/Documents/Github/frontend-perempuanaman/data/wilayahData.js) — complex nested data (provinces → organizational units)

**Frontend page**: `/wilayah` (interactive map with `WilayahMap`, `WilayahStats`, `WilayahList`)

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/wilayah` | 🔓 | All provinces with metadata (for map rendering) |
| GET | `/api/wilayah/:id` | 🔓 | Province detail + nested `wilayah_organisasi` |
| POST | `/api/wilayah` | 🔒 | Add province |
| PUT | `/api/wilayah/:id` | 🔒 | Update province |
| DELETE | `/api/wilayah/:id` | 🔒 | Delete province |
| POST | `/api/wilayah/:id/organisasi` | 🔒 | Add org unit within a province |
| PUT | `/api/wilayah/:id/organisasi/:orgId` | 🔒 | Update org unit |
| DELETE | `/api/wilayah/:id/organisasi/:orgId` | 🔒 | Delete org unit |

**Province shape**:
```json
{
  "id": "sumatera-utara",
  "kodeProvinsi": "12",
  "namaProvinsi": "Sumatera Utara",
  "region": "Sumatera",
  "geo": { "latitude": 2.115, "longitude": 99.545 },
  "map": { "svgId": "ID-SU", "highlightColor": "#FF5733" },
  "statistik": {
    "totalAnggota": 15420,
    "totalWilayahOrganisasi": 45,
    "totalDesa": 120,
    "totalKomunitas": 85
  },
  "statistikUsia": { "pemuda": 5200, "dewasa": 7100, "lansia": 2900 },
  "wilayahOrganisasi": [
    {
      "id": "phd-tano-batak",
      "jenis": "PHD",
      "namaWilayah": "PHD Tano Batak",
      "lokasi": { "kabupatenKota": "Toba", "kecamatan": "Balige", "desa": "..." },
      "statistik": { "jumlahAnggota": 1250, "jumlahKomunitas": 12 },
      "pengurus": { "ketua": "...", "sekretaris": "...", "bendahara": "..." },
      "status": { "aktif": true, "tanggalBerdiri": "2015-08-12" }
    }
  ]
}
```

