## 14. Site Settings & Static Pages

For pages with hardcoded content (Statuta, SOP, Donasi, homepage), create a general settings/pages API:

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/api/settings` | 🔓 | Site-wide config (bank details, contact info, social links) |
| PUT | `/api/settings` | 🔒 | Update settings |
| GET | `/api/pages/:slug` | 🔓 | Get CMS page content (statuta, sop, donasi) |
| PUT | `/api/pages/:slug` | 🔒 | Update page content |

**Settings shape** (for donasi page, sekretariat contact info, etc.):
```json
{
  "siteName": "PEREMPUAN AMAN",
  "contact": {
    "address": "Jl. Tebet Timur Dalam No. 1A, Jakarta Selatan",
    "email": "info@perempuanaman.or.id",
    "phone": "+62 21 8293 7425",
    "operatingHours": "Senin – Jumat, 09.00 – 17.00 WIB"
  },
  "donasi": {
    "bankName": "Bank Mandiri",
    "accountNumber": "123-456-7890",
    "accountHolder": "Yayasan Perempuan Aman",
    "confirmEmail": "donasi@perempuanaman.or.id"
  },
  "socialMedia": { "instagram": "...", "twitter": "...", "youtube": "..." }
}
```

**Pages shape** (for statuta, sop):
```json
{
  "slug": "statuta",
  "title": "Statuta dan ART",
  "content": "<p>HTML content...</p>",
  "pdfUrl": "/uploads/docs/statuta.pdf"
}
```

